[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10764] added new 
``o>>``
, 
``e>>``
, 
``o+e>>``
 redirection operators to append output to an external file
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11191] fixed a redirection bug
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11172] worked on redirection tests
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11144] implemented a spread operator for record literals
fdncred added an experimental 
``stor``
 family of commands for working with in-memory SQLite databases: (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11170] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11194] 2
) and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11135] added a new 
``ExternalResolved``
 syntax shape to show found externals via syntax highlighting in the repl
nibon7 improved error messages and validation for 
``str index-of``
: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11201] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11190] 2
KAAtheWiseGit 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11195] improved 
``input list``
 so it can handle more data types
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11169] forbidded reserved variable names as function arguments
cosineblast 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11182] removed file I/O from some tests that don't need it
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11180] improved 
``nu-protocol``
 so docs build with all features enabled
drbrain 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11173] converted more ShellError variants to named fields
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11171] reverted "Adding support for Polars structs"
rfaulhaber 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11166] bumped 
``sysinfo``
 to 0.29.11
MarikaChlebowska 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11160] improved some filter commands so they preserve metadata
NotLebedev 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11152] improved target expansion in the 
``cp``
 command
sigoden 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11008] fixed spans passed to external_completer
